"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="13412" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a+2b+c = -2 + 4 + c = 2 + c</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이므로</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="4" Style="5"><TEXT CharShape="5"><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079580055" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1225"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5418" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>2 + c leq -23</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="4" Style="5"><TEXT CharShape="5"><CHAR>따라서 정답은 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079580056" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="1226"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2029" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>-23</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="11"><CHAR/></TEXT></P></PARALIST></ENDNOTE></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="10"><CHAR>정의역과 공역이 모두 실수 전체의 집합인 함수<LINEBREAK/><TAB/></CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="60" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079577682" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="204"><SIZE Height="3870" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="11760" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(x) = left { matrix { -2x+1 &amp; left ( x geq b right ) # {c} over {x+a} - 3 &amp; left ( x &lt; b right ) } right .</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR><LINEBREAK/>가 일대일대응이고, 집합 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079577683" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="205"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="12595" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>LEFT { k`|`(f CIRC f)(k)=k RIGHT } = LEFT { alpha ,` beta  RIGHT }</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 이다. </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079577684" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="206"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2562" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>alpha &lt; 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079577685" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="207"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4066" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(alpha) &gt; 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>이고, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079577686" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="208"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2487" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>beta &gt; 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079577687" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="97"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3991" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>f(beta) &lt; 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>일 때, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079577688" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="96"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4216" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a+2b+c</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>의 최댓값을 구하시오. (단, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079577689" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="48"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="525" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>a</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR>, </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="85" BaseUnit="1100" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1079577690" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="47"><SIZE Height="1125" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="450" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true